			<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;">A message from the Superintendent:<p></p></span><br></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;">Brooks Family, I have been on conference calls with TEA and Region 20 Superintendents today regarding COVID-19.  We want to do everything we stop the spread of the virus, so we are announcing that all Brooks Campuses will be closed until Friday, April 24, following our spring break.  There will be no classes, extra-curricular activities, sports, etc.  <p></p></span><br></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;">Please continue to check our, Facebook pages, Remind and Parent Square.  We will have through service for school breakfast and lunch on each campus and we will have at-home packets and online instruction available beginning March 23.  I don't have final details on these arrangements yet, but we will be updating through social media as soon as details are confirmed.  If you have any questions, please feel free to email me at <a href="mailto:Lisa.Schutz@brooksacademy.org" style="color: rgb(3, 59, 115);">Lisa.Schutz@brooksacademy.org</a> - please bear with me as I am receiving many emails at this time and I will answer as quickly as possible.<p></p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;">Lisa Freeman Schutz, M.Ed.<p></p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(241, 245, 248); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;'><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;">Superintendent of Schools</span></p>
